<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, als ir uns
                            <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von
                            <expan>etlich<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> und <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>dien<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>Pet<ex>er</ex></expan> Kragen <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> etc., das
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir wol
                            <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> und <expan>lass<ex>en</ex></expan> ewr
                                <expan>frewnts<ex>chaft</ex></expan>
<expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan>, daz <expan>ders<ex>elb</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>Pet<ex>er</ex></expan> Krag zu disen <expan>zeit<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        niht anheim und mit <expan>etliche<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urgern</ex></expan>
<expan>etwiev<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>auszgeritte<ex>n</ex></expan> ist. Wenn er
                            <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> herheim kombt, so
                            <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> mit im
                                <expan>davo<ex>n</ex></expan> reden und ewch ein
                                <expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>
<expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> tun, ob wir daran gemant
                            <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan>. Denn wo wir
                            <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>frewnts<ex>chaft</ex></expan> lieb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        dienst etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> ii<hi rend="sup">a</hi>
<expan>p<ex>ost</ex></expan> Egidii.</ab>
